हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: After a car accident, a cold and powerful CEO loses his memory and turns into a sweet, obedient "puppy-like" boyfriend. But as his memories return, so do the secrets that could tear their love apart.
